Yes, we've gotta figure out the focus of our future.

20:50.891 --> 20:57.117
But then finally, we also need to recognize this, that faith that God wants us to walk in, it changes everything.

20:58.058 --> 20:58.999
It changes everything.

21:00.301 --> 21:02.943
