21:03.243 --> 21:14.034
For truly I tell you, Jesus says, if you have faith the size of a mustard seed, you will tell this mountain move from here to there.

21:15.618 --> 21:17.021
And it will move."

21:18.663 --> 21:20.547
I would underline that in my Bible if I were you.

21:21.809 --> 21:28.641
And it will move, not might move, not could move, not if you're lucky will move.

21:28.822 --> 21:31.286
No, it will move.

21:31.306 --> 21:37.798
Nothing will be impossible for you.

21:37.818 --> 21:40.082
You see, that's the kind of faith that God wants us to walk in.

21:41.282 --> 21:54.335
