22:23.163 --> 22:29.490
If you've ever had the opportunity of seeing a mustard seed, it's tiny, it's almost microscopic.

22:30.391 --> 22:40.242
And that's why Jesus used that very reference in this passage, because He wanted people to recognize and understand that the smallest little bit of faith

22:41.154 --> 22:44.860
