23:05.730 --> 23:06.691
Just move it out of here.

23:07.071 --> 23:07.852
So I don't have to take that.

23:07.872 --> 23:10.334
I'm not saying, like the mountain's not literally gonna move.

23:10.615 --> 23:21.145
Jesus was using this reference, this incredible illustration to tell us that there's nothing that you will face in your life that God will not bring you through.

23:21.165 --> 23:25.088
If you simply just have that faith.

23:26.269 --> 23:35.378
And I think the importance of this passage of Matthew 17, it helps us to remind us this, is that a lot of times what we do is we sit back and we think that we've gotta have the faith of a mountain to move the mustard seed.

23:36.418 --> 23:37.660
We get it confused.

23:37.740 --> 23:39.002
We get it turned upside down.

23:40.064 --> 23:42.287
We sit here and we face like the smallest of problems.

23:42.327 --> 23:46.274
