23:48.577 --> 23:51.161
God's certainly not going to answer in my prayer.

23:51.182 --> 23:52.263
He's certainly not going to help me.

23:52.323 --> 23:53.465
See, we get this mixed up.

23:53.726 --> 23:56.530
And what I would tell you is this is exactly what Satan wants you to do.

23:57.122 --> 24:05.492
What Satan wants you to do is to believe that you've got to have this big monumental, you know, Billy Graham type faith in order to walk through the challenges of your life.

24:05.512 --> 24:09.277
And here, the God of the universe said this, oh no, that's not true.

24:09.317 --> 24:12.561
What you need is the faith, the size of a mustard seed.

24:14.203 --> 24:16.826
And then all of your doubts and all of your pains.

24:16.906 --> 24:27.058
And even when you're like the disciples who had little faith, like even then, I will be with you and nothing.

24:27.586 --> 24:29.629
will be too hard for you.

