26:08.277 --> 26:19.538
It's moved the right way, it continues to move in the right direction and because of what's happening on the inside, things that I don't understand of how it works, it continues to move and it just keeps on going.

26:20.162 --> 26:25.988
And because of what's happening on the inside, the hands on the outside continue to keep really good time.

26:27.430 --> 26:34.297
