26:34.357 --> 26:36.399
You see, that's the picture of what this quote really says.

26:37.461 --> 26:39.363
What that quote really says is just simply this.

26:39.663 --> 26:47.011
When you get things right on the inside, everything on the outside is just going to work.

26:48.612 --> 26:50.034
What does that mean for us today?

26:51.074 --> 26:58.343
It means make sure that you get things right on the inside, in your faith, walking by faith and not by sight.

26:58.743 --> 27:06.693
And as a result, God will make sure everything on the outside just keeps going.

